This is great, but it is difficult to understand this in context until we compare it to the other models.

To put all of this in English, we are most interested in those that have higher R^2 values and lower BIC, AIC, and RMSE values. According to that knowledge, it looks like Major and Ethnicity are the best predictor for Intrinsic Motivation. Lets see these together, and with that, we can see whether how they relate.
